OL,7,FLouise Ansari, chief executive of
OL,8,FHealthwatch England, said: "We know
OL,9,Fthat public satisfaction with the NHS
OL,10,Fis at record low levels, with too many
OL,11,Fpatients receiving poor care.
OL,13,F"When patients feel their complaints
OL,14,Fare not taken seriously or don't take
OL,15,Fany action due to a complex system,
OL,16,Fservices miss out on vital information
OL,17,Fto help them improve."
