OL,7,F"Ten years on, our research shows that
OL,8,Fthe public still lacks confidence in
OL,9,Fthe NHS complaints system.
OL,11,F"We need a step change in how people's
OL,12,Fcomplaints are handled and acted on.
OL,13,FHealthcare leaders should focus on
OL,14,Fdeveloping a culture of listening and
OL,15,Flearning from complaints across the
OL,16,Fsector.
