OL,7,F"Making it easier for patients and
OL,8,Ffamilies to navigate the complaints
OL,9,Fsystem through the NHS app, setting
OL,10,Fmandatory response times, and
OL,11,Fmeasuring people's satisfaction with
OL,12,Fthe process and the outcomes from
OL,13,Fcomplaints, will be a key part of
OL,14,Fthis."
