OL,7,FAn NHS spokesman said: "Every patient
OL,8,Fdeserves high-quality care, and NHS
OL,9,Fstaff are working tirelessly to
OL,10,Frespond to the increasing demand for
OL,11,Fservices ` with a record number of
OL,12,Fpatients coming forward in both
OL,13,Fprimary care and hospitals in the past
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,F"The NHS takes patient experiences
OL,17,Fvery seriously and we are committed to
OL,18,Flistening to patients and rolling out
OL,19,Finitiatives like Martha's Rule, which
OL,20,Fis already having a transformative
OL,21,Feffect in some cases.
