OL,7,F"This report highlights that there is
OL,8,Fstill more to do to listen to
OL,9,Fpatients, respond to complaints and
OL,10,Fimprove services, which is why the NHS
OL,11,Fis working closely with the Government
OL,12,Fon this year's 10-Year Health Plan to
OL,13,Fhelp us transform services to provide
OL,14,Fthe best quality care for patients."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,17,FHealth and Social Care said: "This
OL,18,Freport shows the NHS complaints system
OL,19,Fis failing far too many patients.
