OL,7,F"We are determined to foster an
OL,8,Fenvironment where patients and NHS
OL,9,Fstaff alike are able to speak up,
OL,10,Fknowing they will be supported and
OL,11,Fthat their concerns will be listened
OL,12,Fto and acted upon.
OL,14,F"We must never turn a blind eye to
OL,15,Ffailure, which is why we will build a
OL,16,Fculture of transparency in the NHS and
OL,17,Fensure patients voices are heard."
